00:39:19,950 --> 00:39:21,518
<font color="#00ff40">Rasa sakit yang kau sebutkan !</font>

720
00:39:21,585 --> 00:39:22,886
<font color="#00ff40">Semua kesedihan itu !</font>

721
00:39:22,953 --> 00:39:23,891
<font color="#00ff40">Kau membunuh ibuku.</font>

722
00:39:24,011 --> 00:39:25,588
<font color="#00ff40">Tidak ! /
Kau membunuhnya !</font>

723
00:39:26,715 --> 00:39:29,927
<font color="#00ff40">Bayi itu-- atau apalah
namanya, sudah membunuhnya !</font>

724
00:39:33,966 --> 00:39:35,400
<font color="#00ff40">Aku tak bisa bersamamu.</font>

725
00:39:35,468 --> 00:39:37,819
<font color="#00ff40">Aku tak ingin bersamamu..</font>

726
00:39:39,272 --> 00:39:42,040
<font color="#00ff40">Apa maksud perkataanmu ?</font>

727
00:39:42,108 --> 00:39:43,346
<font color="#00ff40">Kubilang, Menjauhlah.</font>

728
00:39:43,466 --> 00:39:44,506
<font color="#00ff40">Apa ?</font>

729
00:39:44,764 --> 00:39:46,932
<font color="#00ff40">Tidak, Jangan lakukan ini !</font>

730
00:39:47,052 --> 00:39:48,134
<font color="#00ff40">Menjauhlah, Tate.</font>

731
00:39:48,254 --> 00:39:51,116
<font color="#00ff40">Kau yang kuinginkan !
Kau yang kumiliki !</font>

732
00:39:51,183 --> 00:39:52,550
<font color="#00ff40">Menjauhlah ! /
Tidak !</font>

733
00:39:52,670 --> 00:39:54,964
<font color="#00ff40"><i>Menjauhlah !</i></font>

734
00:40:33,232 --> 00:40:36,062
<font color="#00ff40">Tadi itu sangat berani...</font>

735
00:40:36,129 --> 00:40:37,570
<font color="#00ff40">Aku bangga padamu.</font>

736
00:40:37,827 --> 00:40:39,351
<font color="#00ff40">Bu...</font>

737
00:40:39,749 --> 00:40:41,472
<font color="#00ff40">Maafkan aku, Bu.</font>

738
00:40:41,730 --> 00:40:43,638
<font color="#00ff40">Aku sangat menyesal,
Kau harus meninggal...</font>

739
00:40:43,758 --> 00:40:45,524
<font color="#00ff40">Shh.</font>

740
00:40:45,829 --> 00:40:48,501
<font color="#00ff40">Aku menyesal, Kau kehilangan bayimu...</font>

741
00:40:56,214 --> 00:40:59,522
<font color="#00ff40">Tapi aku tak kehilangan gadis kecilku...</font>

